      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "# Ideogram 4 Models\n\n# [Comfy Ideogram4](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Ideogram-4/tree/main)\n-------------------\n\n# KJ Nodes Pack Required\n\n# [KJ Node Pack](https://github.com/kijai/ComfyUI-KJNodes)\n-------------------\n\n# YouTube junk on how to use KJ Prompt Builder\n\n#  [YouTube NEW BEST OMG IT MAKES BOOBS! Tutorials](https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=ideogram+kj+prompt+builder)\n-------------------\n\n# Settings are for a for a softer look and feel. you can change CFG/CFG Override + Start Percent/Steps/Shift, and sheduler/sampler.\n\n# Increase CFG/Override to get a crisper look as well as use Euler or er_sde. Euler A gives a softer look.\n\n# Shift helps, I have not played much with that. Go crazy.\n\n# Flash Attention nodes are bypassed if you have FA installed you can use them for more speed."
